about: What it is:A duo that’s your go-to for a quick, full-coverage, face lift-effect while maracuja juicy lip hydrates and visibly plumps for juicy lips...Ingredient Callouts:Free of parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, sulfates SLS & SLES, triclocarban, and triclosan. reviews.review_text: The lip-gloss is free -I tried it and I approve! I like it better than other lip products I have The concealer is always a good choice to hide my blemishes.

reviews.review_buyer_description: Brown eyes, brown hair, Light skin tone, Combination skin
reviews.review_text: My friend had me try the lip plump on a night out (I forgot my gloss), and let me tell you… I FELL IN LOVE. You’re only paying for the shape tape and it’s free. Literally, girl math at its finest.
